These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, thriller, documentary, fantasy
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, fishing, reading, collecting
House: art-deco, craftsman, futuristic, cape-cod
City: berlin, san-francisco, nizza, boston
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
 3. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the futuristic house is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the craftsman house is the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to berlin is between the person traveling to boston and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
10. the person watching horror movies is the person traveling to boston##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | documentary  | horror    | fantasy    | thriller   |
| Hobby   | fishing     | singing   | reading       | collecting    |
| House   | craftsman | art-deco | cape-cod    | futuristic |
| City           | san-francisco | boston       | berlin | nizza     |

