.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
House: palace, victorian, wooden, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, pop, electronic, folk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, siglo, cain, alhambra
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, sprite, iced-tea
 1. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
 2. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 3. the fan of pop is on the right of the wooden house##1
 4. the victorian house is the aristoff-smoker##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the palace house##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 7. the futuristic house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
10. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
11. the cain-smoker is the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| House          | palace  | victorian    | wooden     | futuristic       |
| Music-Genre         | electronic | folk | punk   | pop |
| Cigar   | cain | aristoff   | siglo   | alhambra    |
| Beverage         | sprite | iced-tea  | coffee | cola   |

