 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person playing whist is the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the person playing whist is the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
