.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, french, indonesian, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, bird, dog
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, may, april
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, ritmeester, bluemaster, cain
 1. the chinese is the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
 5. the french is the cain-smoker##1
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the chinese##1
 7. the pakistani is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the indonesian is the owner of the dog##1
12. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani       | indonesian   | chinese   | french   |
| Pet       | chinchilla        | dog | fish    | bird       |
| Birthday      | april | march    | may  | november |
| Cigar      | ritmeester  | bluemaster  | bongani | cain    |

