.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, rose, marigold, daisy
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, monopoly, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, guinea-pig, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, tram, van, boat
 1. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person playing monopoly is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who growsdaisy##2
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 6. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
 7. the person who growsrose is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
12. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Flower    | marigold    | daisy      | amaryllis          | rose    |
| Game   | snooker | scrabble       | monopoly | chess |
| Pet     | bird     | guinea-pig      | turtle     | goldfish |
| Transport   | tram   | boat | van        | helicopter   |

