4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dannemann, baccarat, bongani
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, mauve, white, pink
 1. the pilot is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 3. the dancer is on the right of the architect##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
 6. the bongani-smoker is between the person who likes white and the dannemann-smoker##2
 7. the baccarat-smoker is the pilot##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the pilot##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes red is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby      | fishing  | rock-climbing    | board-games       | skydiving       |
| Job          | freelancer    | pilot | architect | dancer     |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | baccarat        | bongani    | dannemann   |
| Color   | red  | white      | pink    | mauve |

