 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
 5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 7. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the baccarat-smoker is between the person drinking milk and the fan of d&b##2
10. the person playing whist is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
12. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
