 4. the townhouse house is between the person who's birthday is in february and the modern house##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the cottage house and the modern house##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food      | peas   | pomegranate   | cucumber     | zucchini   |
| House   | cottage  | townhouse       | modern | wooden |
| Birthday           | february     | january   | june     | august     |
| City         | venice | prague | marseilles   | edinburgh |

