.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, september, march
4 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, guinea-pig, chinchilla
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, carrot, watermelon
City: liverpool, marseilles, rome, venice
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person eating mango is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
10. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person eating watermelon is in an odd position##4
12. the owner of the mouse is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday      | september       | january | february        | march        |
| Pet         | chinchilla | guinea-pig       | mouse | horse |
| Food   | watermelon     | mango        | cabbage    | carrot      |
| City         | marseilles     | rome    | venice | liverpool   |

