.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigoldpy, zinnia, marigold, rose
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, poker, backgammon
House: palace, wooden, futuristic, modern
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, black, yellow, lavender
 1. the person who growsrose is the futuristic house##1
 2. the futuristic house is between the person playing chess and the person playing backgammon##2
 3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 4. the person who likes black is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the palace house is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is the wooden house##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 8. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
 9. the wooden house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
10. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
11. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
12. the person who growsmarigoldpy is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower   | zinnia      | marigoldpy | rose     | marigold        |
| Game   | poker | backgammon  | bridge     | chess |
| House         | wooden    | palace | futuristic      | modern |
| Color     | lavender | black     | yellow | fuchsia       |

 